            <div class="project">
                <h2>Atm Interface</h2>
                <p>[The ATM Interface Project focuses on designing and implementing an intuitive and secure user interface for Automated Teller Machines (ATMs). The interface serves as a user-friendly gateway to banking transactions, enabling customers to conveniently access their accounts and perform various financial activities. Key features include secure card insertion, PIN authentication, transaction selection (withdrawals, deposits, transfers, balance inquiries), cash dispensing, receipt printing, language options, accessibility considerations, error handling, and robust session management. The project aims to enhance user experience, streamline banking operations, and uphold data security while adhering to modern design principles and efficient backend integration.]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h2>Library Management System</h2>
                <p>[A Library Management System (LMS) is a software project designed to streamline the organization, tracking, and management of library resources and operations. It serves as a digital platform for librarians, staff, and patrons to efficiently handle various library-related tasks. The system's primary goal is to enhance the overall library experience by automating processes and providing easy access to information.A Library Management System modernizes traditional library practices, enabling efficient resource management, improved user experience, and better utilization of library resources. It plays a pivotal role in making library services more accessible, convenient, and engaging for both library staff and patrons]</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project">
                <h2>Number Guessing Game</h2>
                <p>The "Number Guessing Game" project involves creating an interactive and entertaining game where players attempt to guess a randomly chosen number within a specified range.This project aims to provide an enjoyable and interactive experience for players of all ages while showcasing proficiency in user interface design, random number generation, user input validation, and conditional logic. It offers an opportunity to practice programming skills and create a simple yet engaging game application. </p>
